name: Pastel Polka Dots
gradient: radial-gradient(circle, #ffafbd 10%, transparent 10%, transparent 20%), radial-gradient(circle, #ffc3a0 10%, transparent 10%, transparent 20%)

name: Blurred Stripes
gradient: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255, 94, 98, 0.5), rgba(255, 94, 98, 0)), linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255, 182, 98, 0.5), rgba(255, 182, 98, 0))

name: Gradient Beads
gradient: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, #00c6ff, transparent 20%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, #0072ff, transparent 20%)

name: Ocean Ripples
gradient: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 198, 255, 0.5), rgba(0, 114, 255, 0.5)), radial-gradient(circle, #00c6ff, transparent)

name: Speckled Glow
gradient: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 50%, #56ab2f, #a8e063, transparent 70%), radial-gradient(circle at 70% 50%, #ffafbd, #ffc3a0, transparent 70%)

name: Gradient Arches
gradient: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #00c6ff, transparent 40%), radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #0072ff, transparent 60%)

name: Crisscross Glow
gradient: repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, #ff7e5f, #feb47b 10px, transparent 10px, transparent 20px), repeating-linear-gradient(to right, #ff7e5f, #feb47b 10px, transparent 10px, transparent 20px)

name: Overlapping Circles
gradient: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, #56ab2f, transparent 40%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, #a8e063, transparent 40%)
